  "remarks": "Has ties to numerous senior Al-Qaida (QDe.004) leaders. Wanted by the\nSaudi Arabian Government for terrorism. Father's name is Abdullah Razeeq al Mouled al\nSbhua. Physical description: eye colour: dark; hair colour: dark; complexion: dark.\nSpeaks Arabic. Photo available for inclusion in the INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special\nNotice.  Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.  INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
